        </div>

        <!-- FAQs -->
        <div id="doc-faqs" class="doc-content">
            <h3>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)</h3>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>Q: The bot is not responding to my commands.</h4>
                <p>
                    <strong>A:</strong> First, check if the bot has the correct
                    permissions. If it does, try kicking and re-inviting the bot
                    to your server. This often resolves permission issues.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>Q: How can I change the bot's prefix?</h4>
                <p>
                    <strong>A:</strong> Currently, the prefix is fixed. However,
                    we are working on a customizable prefix feature that will be
                    available in a future update.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h4>Q: Can I suggest a new feature?</h4>
                <p>
                    <strong>A:</strong> We appreciate your feedback. Use the
                    command !reqfitur to submit your feature request directly to
                    the owner.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
